1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Welcome. This is a local subtitle sample for the backpacking video.
欢迎。这是为背包徒步视频准备的本地字幕示例。

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
Tap any subtitle line to repeat just that sentence.
点击任意字幕行，只重复播放这一句。

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:13,000
Use English only when you want to practice listening and shadowing.
想练听力和跟读时，可以只显示英文。

4
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:18,000
Turn on bilingual subtitles when you need the Chinese meaning.
需要理解中文意思时，可以打开双语字幕。

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:24,000
Later, this screen can load subtitles generated by Whisper or imported from SRT files.
后续这个页面可以加载 Whisper 生成的字幕，或者导入 SRT 字幕文件。
